00:21:34.450 --> 00:21:37.690
Using that data, then you
can find the right length,

00:21:37.690 --> 00:21:42.420
complexity, visual appeal, and
difficulty to build your game.

00:21:42.420 --> 00:21:44.170
You don't want to cut
corners, because you

00:21:44.170 --> 00:21:50.310
